      "span_text": "How exactly the GT view helps in knowledge acquisition has been discussed at some length by Bylander and Chandrasekaran [CITATION_1] , but the idea is simple: the knowledge and inference primitives directly give the knowledge engineer a vocabulary in terms of which to seek both the declarative and control knowledge in the domain for the task."
